1.10
log
@Add support for root on nfs using v3. Code adapted from NetBSD.
Tested on sparc by miod, octeon by aalm and armv7 by me.
miod ok.
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: nfsdiskless.h,v 1.9 2013/04/17 16:22:24 florian Exp $	*/
